  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.27,
      "end": 4.45,
      "text": "Lesson 93–Our New Neighbour.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第93课——我们的新邻居。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 6.07,
      "end": 10.57,
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 12.05,
      "end": 14.77,
      "text": "Why is Nigel a lucky man?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "奈杰尔为什么是个幸运的人？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 17.66,
      "end": 20.56,
      "text": "Nigel is our new next-door neighbour.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "奈杰尔是我们新搬来的隔壁邻居。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 21.62,
      "end": 22.86,
      "text": "He's a pilot.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他是一名飞行员。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 24.1,
      "end": 26.06,
      "text": "He was in the RAF.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他曾在英国皇家空军服役。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 27.64,
      "end": 31.34,
      "text": "He will fly to New York next month.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "下个月他将飞往纽约。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 33.18,
      "end": 36.94,
      "text": "The month after next, he'll fly to Tokyo.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "再下个月，他将飞往东京。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 38.46,
      "end": 41.24,
      "text": "At the moment, he's in Madrid.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "此刻他在马德里。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 42.28,
      "end": 45,
      "text": "He flew to Spain a week ago.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他一星期前飞去了西班牙。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 46.58,
      "end": 50.54,
      "text": "He'll return to London the week after next.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他将在下下个星期返回伦敦。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 51.54,
      "end": 61.86,
      "text": "He's only 41 years old, and he has already been to nearly every country in the world.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他只有41岁，却已经去过世界上几乎每一个国家。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 63.76,
      "end": 69.74,
      "text": "Nigel is a very lucky man, but his wife isn't very lucky.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "奈杰尔是个非常幸运的人，但他的妻子并不幸运。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 70.54,
      "end": 73.02,
      "text": "She usually stays at home.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "她通常待在家里。"
      }
    }
  ]
}
